Little did you know, /pet guard here turn and face pet, now summon armor and let your pet invis, then hand armor/weaps to him while he's invised.  Also works with sporlit in RE (the thing that makes the sporelings appear when you run through it), A Mystical Voice (at any nexus porting spire), and several other things.  Untargettable, but if you know where they are you can target them by opening a trade window with them.<br>
<br>
Then you stand there at the spire with your pet and pretend to be a monk practicing instill doubt (hit attack, and swing into the air).  Careful though, saw a monk get owned by A Mystical Voice one night, though it's never attacked me back, I think a GM decided to have some fun (since there was a gm at that spire right before that monk started getting owned).<br>
<br>
